    • enable

      public void enable()
      Convenience method to enable the cell module with bare minimum default values and a default configuration for CAMs using the DEFAULT_CAM_GEO_RADIUS Note: When using this method, no bitrates will be set and default values configured in the Cell module will be used. If you want to set these values use enable(CellModuleConfiguration)
